  LINUX   : http://standards.freedesktop.org/autostart-spec/autostart-spec-latest.html
  OSX     : http://developer.apple.com/documentation/MacOSX/Conceptual/BPSystemStartup/Articles/CustomLogin.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/20002134-SW2
